  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Up to 10 infants will complete the study aimed to establish a technique for measuring whole
      body adiposity and brown adipose tissue in infant subjects using dual energy x-ray
      absorptiometry and magnetic resonance imaging, respectively.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
